OL,3,CMen charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter man hospitalised with serious
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FTwo men have been charged with
OL,8,Fattempted murder after another man was
OL,9,Fseriously injuried in Solihull.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to an address on
OL,12,FHeathmere Drive shortly before 5am on
OL,13,FTuesday 7th April.
OL,15,FThey found a man in his 20s with head
OL,16,Finjuries. He was taken to hospital in
OL,17,Fa serious condition, where he remains.
OL,19,FTwo men were arrested and have been
OL,20,Fcharged with attempted murder in
OL,21,Fconnection with the incident.
