OL,3,CMen charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter man hospitalised with serious
OL,5,Cinjuries
OL,7,FBen Edwards, 26, and Dean Edwards, 30,
OL,8,Fboth from Solihull, were remanded to
OL,9,Fappear before Birmingham Magistrates
OL,10,FCourt today.
OL,12,FWest Midlands Police said: "We're
OL,13,Fcontinuing to appeal for information
OL,14,Fand you can contact us via Live Chat
OL,15,Fon our website, or by calling 101, and
OL,16,Fquote log 497 of 7 April."
